ilt joystick forward to enable dynamic dragon motion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enable Glider Speed x3 (via cheats with TOTK Optimizer or TKMM)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use Glider Speed cheat (tap A) with dynamic dragon motion&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Manually install the “All in One” TKMM file&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Optional:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Infinite stamina cheat for extended flight&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Moon jump cheat for upward gliding&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/480138"&gt;Ultracam mod&lt;/a&gt; (by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2745192" data-id="member_2745192"&gt;MaxLastBreath&lt;/a&gt;) or other FOV mods&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is mod is easily compatible with other animation mods with TKMM.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;UPDATE:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="SelectedElement"&gt;Demon Lord Gleeok from Challenge Mode has been added!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Demon Lord Gleeok is only compatible with Challenge Mode&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Use TKMM to merge mods together&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
