      <title>TRUE NG+ &amp; URL TO BEST UNBREAKABLE WEAPONS MOD</title>
      <author>Porroman420</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/601559</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/601559#PostsListModule</comments>
