fixed by Robbie, but after that, all photos are gonna be there)&lt;br&gt;- all locations discovered (fast travel between out in the world shrines enabled, still need to complete the tutorial to unlock the travel as usual, quest hidden shrines are still locked, enabling them breaks their quest)&lt;br&gt;- 4500 zonai charges&lt;br&gt;- some ruppees&lt;br&gt;- some poes&lt;br&gt;- complete map unlocked (all towers - to fast travel between towers you need to "activate" them, only the map is aviable, 119 lightroots)&lt;br&gt;- you can buy 10 hearts/ 2 full stamina wheels at the demon statue to unlock the 5th sage or the master sword early without doing any shrine beside the ones at the tutorial or any boss&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;!!!BE WARY, SOME OF THE STRONGEST ENEMY VARIATONS ARE ROAMING THE LAND !!!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;i do changed a lot of things to make it feel like a proper ng+, while retaining others that could make the whole experience shallow and kinda empty, most ng+ files out there just give you everything and end up breaking stuff later in the game, with this save you can do EVERYTHING you can do in a normal savefile, but now you have some goodies and some extras for your new adventure&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also if you want a more "classic" zelda experience check out this other mod i made (imo i hate the durability sytem since always)&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/601874"&gt;THE SWORD THAT SEALS THE DARKNESS&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;enjoy !&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
