      <guid isPermaLink="false">e65b468558b692ac15f1ce59d6c4b5f9875b057d</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Jun 2025 06:52:02 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/647c697a272ec.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/649e7ce03460b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; What I could salvage&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Addition&lt;/em&gt;: Uploaded several true replacements with full physics that I *think* work properly&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Change&lt;/em&gt;: I lost all my TOTK mod folders in a boating accident so I honestly don't know anymore&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Simple model edits to make Korok hunting a less goofy experience.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Removes the silly leaf mask from the Korok Mask, or completely replaces the model with another headpiece of your choosing to match your favorite look.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;I wanted to keep this simple, and compatible with any other equipment mods, so I didn't touch the resource size table. All the edits are contained solely in the armor actor files, which unfortunately means some of the model swaps are partially missing hair physics, but it is what it is.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The animation still plays on the pinwheel, and the audio que is intact across every option. &lt;i&gt;Please note that model swaps are purely cosmetic, they offer no set bonuses or defensive attributes.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Available Options:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Korok Mask Without Mask  (&lt;i&gt;Mask Removed, Bun and Pinwheel Only&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Default Hair  (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;No Rear Hair Physics&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. Hairband  (&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;No Ponytail Physics&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. Cap of the Wild  (&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;No Top Hair Physic&lt;/i&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; - &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;hardly noticeable!&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; )&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Cap of Time  (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Full Physics Support&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6. Fierce Deity Mask  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Full Physics and Material Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;7. Dark Hood  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Full Physics and Material Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;8. Cap of the Wind  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Full Physics Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9. Cap of the Hero  (&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;i&gt;Full Physics Support&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10. Cap of the Sky  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;No Hair Physics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;11. Cap of Twilight  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;No Hair Physics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;12. Sheik Mask  (&lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;No Hair Physics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Compatibility:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Compatible with all game versions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Will not conflict with hair texture mods, or any other mod that doesn't directly modify &lt;b&gt;Armor_176.Armor_176_Head.bfres.mc&lt;/b&gt; or &lt;b&gt;Armor_176_Head.pack.zs&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Versions of the files that are compatible with &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/446417"&gt;Non-Upgradeable Armor Defense Increase&lt;/a&gt; are included in a sub folder in the download. Defense is set to 9, same as the mod. Replace &lt;b&gt;Armor_176_Head.pack.zs&lt;/b&gt; in that mod, or just delete it and use the one in Korok Transmog.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;u&gt;Installation Instructions:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Open the .zip, choose which version you want, and place it in your mod folder, same as any other mod&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://i.imgur.com/XLl4aEL.gif" width="60%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.dictionary.com/e/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/Thinking_Face_Emoji-Emoji-Island.png" width="5%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/korok_mask_transmogrifier_nuadi.zip" type="application/zip"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/korok_mask_true_replacements.zip" type="application/zip"/>
